attributes.title: Tennis Balls (3-Pack Tube)
attributes.description:
Created on February 24, 2010 by Gtg501r on Sourcemap.org:

Tennis Balls (3-Pack Tube)   Most tennis balls are manufactured in SE Asia due to the local availability of natural rubber.  Wilson uses 25% recycled PET in packaging.
